- `uv run pytest tests/units` ā†’ 2044 passed, 12 skipped, 2 failed.
- The 2 failures are pre-existing and unrelated
  (`tests/units/api/test_external_api.py::TestDomainVersions::{test_versions_not_found,test_versions_success}`
  ā€” "Registry not configured" in the offline test env; present before this change).
- Changes are shell (Makefile/deploy.sh) + docs only ā€” no Python touched; verified
  via `bash -n scripts/deploy.sh` and `make -n` dry-runs confirming CONFIG resolves
  to `scripts/deploy.config.sh` (default) and `scripts/deploy.config.moneypool.sh`
